```
CREATE TABLE dog
(
    dog_id            int,
    dog_name          varchar(50) UNIQUE,
    owner_id          int,
    breed_id          int,
    veterinarian_id   int,
    PRIMARY KEY (dog_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (owner_id) REFERENCES owner(owner_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (breed_id) REFERENCES breed(breed_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (veterinarian_id) REFERENCES veterinarian(veterinarian_id)
);
```
